milestones.description: Nayan Mongia has broken the record for most dismissals (91) in ODIs for IND, going past Kiran More's 90
This is the highest match aggregate (577) involving teams Australia & India in ODIs
Azharuddin has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (274), going past Allan Border
Azharuddin has broken the record for most catches (128) in ODIs, going past Allan Border's 127
